\FF[ama_laugh]Amma: "We've got to become friends with Urigawa again,
y'know♪"

\F[beni_mizugi1]Akane: "I'd like to keep the policewoman on our side... If
any naughty kids try to escape from the academy, we'll need
her to catch them..."

\F[beni_mizugi1]Akane: "So, I want Kikyo-san to go over there, but... what
to do..."

\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[kikyou_smile]\AA[2]Kikyo: "Ah, Suzaku-san. This is my older sister. She's been
patrolling for us."
\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[kikyou_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Nice to meet you."

\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[momoha_smile]\AA[2]Momoha: "The pleasure is mine. Kikyo has been in your care.
She tends to rush into things... must be tough, right?"
\F[beni_mizugi3]\FF[momoha_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "No... it's not like that..."
\FF[kikyou_trouble]Kikyo: "Sister, you shouldn't trouble a friend..."

\F[momoha_smile]\FF[kikyou_trouble]\AA[1]Momoha: "It's just an inquiry. If Kikyo is causing trouble,
as her sister, I want to know about it."
\F[momoha_smile]\FF[kikyou_trouble]\AA[2]Kikyo: "Th-that's what I mean by troubling...!"

\F[beni_mizugi3]\FF[kikyou_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "Kikyo, do you have trouble dealing with your
sister?"

\F[beni_mizugi3]\FF[kikyou_angry]\AA[2]Kikyo: "Trouble!? Not at all!! I always respect her and
she's my goal!! I always...!!"

\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[kikyou_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Your dream is to be a policewoman, right? You want
to be like your sister!"
\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[kikyou_trouble]\AA[2]Kikyo: "Ugh...!!"
\F[momoha_smile]\FF[kikyou_trouble]\AA[1]Momoha: "Oh... I see... (intently)"
\F[momoha_smile]\FF[kikyou_trouble]\AA[2]Kikyo: "It's... embarrassing..."

\F[momoha_smile]\FF[kikyou_trouble]\AA[2]Kikyo: "Don't look at me with those eyes... please!!
Sister...!! Ahh...!!"
\F[beni_mizugi3]Akane: "Ah... she ran away."

\F[beni_mizugi3]\FF[momoha_smile]\AA[2]Momoha: "She's always been shy. And her impulsiveness hasn't
changed either. I'm still worried about her."
\F[beni_mizugi3]\FF[momoha_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "I'm worried too."

\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[momoha_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Having someone like you as her role model... I doubt
Kikyo will grow up to be a fine lady♪"
\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[momoha_trouble]\AA[2]Momoha: "Eh...?"

\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[momoha_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "That's why you need to change into a suitable figure
too♪ Behind the pillar... so Kikyo won't find you♪"
\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[momoha_trouble]\AA[2]Momoha: "What do you mean...? Eh... eehh...!? "

\F[beni_mizugi1]\FF[momoha_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "Change and... become one of us...!! Let's be useful
to our master!!"

Momoha: "You plan to attack a policewoman!? Aahh!! Wh-what
is thisss...♪"
Momoha: "Ahahahaahnn... The slimy stuff is..."
Momoha: "Becoming a sister worthy of Kikyo... for meee♪"
Momoha: "Aaaaahhh... kuhiiiiinnn♪"
